    "Management": {
      "text": "Ill-appearing\nAnalgesia\nIVF\nAntibiotics\nUrgent surgical consultation\nWell-appearing\nAntibiotics\nCiprofloxacin\n750mg PO BID AND\nmetronidazole\n500mg QID x7d\nOutpatient surgery referral\nImproperly excised fistulas may result in permanent fecal incontinence\nSpasm treatment\nNitroglycerin\n,\nLidocaine\nSitz baths",
